  <h2>About</h2>

  <div class="row">
    <section class="col-xs-12">
	<h4>The purpose of Binder is to be a platform to connect students at the University of North Dakota to buy and sell second-hand text books.</h4>
	
    <br />
   
    <h4>Created by the senior class of ISBC490 in Spring of 2017, this project is envisioned to eventually be apart of the UND.edu website; hence, is designed to look similar to the university's main website.</h4>
    
    <br />
    
    <h4>This web application can only be accessed by individuals with an UND.edu email address. While Binder only cater for the College of Business and Public Administration currently, it will be eventually be expanded to all other colleges throughout the campus.</h4>
    
    <br />
    
    <h4>Thank you for your support and patience; we hope you'll be connected to your next textbook, with ease.</h4>
    
